will act on is from the current position to the position that would
be achieved by using the movement command.
:LI.A search command:
:UL compact.
:LI./ (forward slash)
:LI.? (question mark)
:LI.n
:LI.N
:eUL.
See the section
:HDREF refid='srching'.
